eadings><font color=#A0B0E0>Comment</font></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uubergnome563.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ubergnome563</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/3/02 6:34:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2016.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> heh here is class balance for you...</span><hr size=1> Infiltrator vs Night shade:  i usually one shot blue ones if i get cs on them.  There is NO blue nightshade that can melee me to death.  I always end up with 60% health after a straight melee fight with a blue nightshade <br><br>Infiltrator vs Shadowblade:  blue sb kills me in 4 non CS with a 2 handed sword, and i have in excess of 950 hp.  He had about 60% health left after the fight.<br><br>Balanced?  You tell me...<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usneekeerz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>sneekeerz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/3/02 6:56:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2016.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: heh here is class balance for you...</span><hr size=1> 2 handers outdamages dual wield by alot =/.<br><br>You have 50 in CS, so I guess your envenom is pretty gimped. Using lesser enervating, i can win a yellow SB in a toe to toe fight, with no Cs opener on both sides.<br><br>Thier weapons are str based, enervating will take off huge chunks of thier str. They fight like a girl after that, especially the kobolds <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.